name: Golden Spiral
description:
🔌Golden Spiral is a plugin that calculates the golden ratio sequence and creates layers.

⚙️Calculate : Enter a value in the input box at the top right to calculate it.

✨Generate : Press the Generate button to generate a layer that fits the golden sequence.
